{{Infobox Berry |name = Rabuta |image = [[File:Rabuta.png]] |caption = Even though it is bitter, it should be eaten peel and all. The hair on the peel cleans the stomach from the inside. |growtime = 3h 24m 0s |harvest = 28 berries |replant = 10% |points = 600 |flavor = {{!}} 0 {{!}} 0 {{!}} 0 {{!}} 20 {{!}} 10 }} '''Rabuta''' is a type of [[Berries|Berry]] that can be planted in [[Farm]]. It can be obtained by surrounding an [[Aspear]] with at least 1 [[Aguav]]. The [[Aspear]] will then have a chance to mutate into this berry.
